  m_text: In the maze devoid of light, darkness will lead the way. Beware, tis' a
    journey not for the hearts of gold. Amidst the chaos, find the diamond in the
    rough. Within the deepest abyss, a gemstone glows. It hungers for what glitters...
    Enter the gates and unleash it from its eternal prison.
